{"tid":2280890,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國再制裁香港公司 指資助伊朗軍事公司採購敏感貨品","createTime":"2020-11-11T00:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T11:21:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc0d4de12285d9f096cac864c368c8d0c91edee","tid":2280890,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T00:10:46.000Z","msg":"美國再制裁香港公司 指之助伊朗軍事公司採購敏感貨品<br />\n<br />\n美國周二宣佈制裁六間公司和四人，包括一間香港公司，指之違反美國對伊朗制裁令。<br />\n<br />\n財政部指那些人和公司涉嫌協助伊朗軍事公司Iran Communication Industries（ICI）採購美國電子零件及其他敏感貨品。被歐美列入黑名單的ICI，從事軍事通訊系統和導彈發射器生產。<br />\n<br />\n財長姆欽（Steven Mnuchin）指伊朗利用全球公司網絡，發展具破壞性的軍事能力。<br />\n<br />\n被制裁的香港公司為中易實業有限公司（Proma Industry Co., Ltd.），被指從2016年起協助將總值數萬美元的貨物，運到ICI旗下設於伊朗的公司Hoda Trading。Hoda Trading也在制裁名單上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201111/BQZCNFAEVFEY7J7HCXZHRUMWOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201111%2FBQZCNFAEVFEY7J7HCXZHRUMWOY%2F&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=1d678e4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201111%2FBQZCNFAEVFEY7J7HCXZHRUMWOY%2F&h=c5ca38d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201111/BQZCNFAEVFEY7J7HCXZHRUMWOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n全文請前往蘋果"},{"pid":"caa461928fd4007e2bb5f14530897704819adde8","tid":2280890,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T00:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20121309db5602295e734f5257a6bc109bbd23fc","tid":2280890,"uid":38572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T00:15:52.000Z","msg":"日日出手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}